---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
import DashboardMockup from '../components/DashboardMockup.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-border-soft/60 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur">
    <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1320px] items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="logo-wordmark text-xl text-dark">karteo<span class="logo-dot">.</span></span>
      </a>
      <div class="hidden items-center gap-8 md:flex">
        <a href="#pilar-01" class="text-sm text-subtle transition hover:text-body">Por que Karteo</a>
        <a href="#como-funciona" class="text-sm text-subtle transition hover:text-body">Como funciona</a>
        <a href="#precos" class="text-sm text-subtle transition hover:text-body">Preços</a>
      </div>
      <a href="#cta" class="rounded-lg bg-teal px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-teal-hover">
        Agendar demo
      </a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(13,148,136,0.12),transparent_55%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,rgba(99,102,241,0.08),transparent_50%)]"></div>
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[1320px] items-center gap-12 px-6 py-20 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_1fr] lg:gap-20 lg:py-28">
      <div>
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-teal/20 bg-teal-pale/60 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-teal">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal"></span>
          Plataforma para assessores e planejadores
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-[42px] font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-tight text-dark md:text-[56px]">
          Se você cobra <span class="text-teal">R$ 5 mil</span> por planejamento, está cobrando barato.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl italic text-teal md:text-2xl">
          — pelo menos, com o Karteo.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-subtle">
          O material justifica o seu ticket. A plataforma cuida do resto.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="#cta" class="rounded-lg bg-teal px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-teal-hover">
            Agendar demonstração
          </a>
          <a href="#pilar-01" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-surface px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-body transition hover:border-teal/40 hover:bg-bg-page">
            Veja por quê
            <span class="transition group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <DashboardMockup variant="hero" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CALCULADORA: segmentada por perfil -->
  <section id="calculadora" class="border-t border-border-soft bg-bg-page py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1100px] px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-teal">Calculadora</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-dark md:text-4xl">
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="planejador">Quanto vale a <span class="text-teal">sua hora</span> de planejamento?</span>
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="consultor">Quanto vale a <span class="text-teal">sua hora</span> de consultoria?</span>
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="assessor">Quanto você <span class="text-teal">perde por ano</span> em churn?</span>
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="outro">Quanto vale a <span class="text-teal">sua hora</span> de trabalho?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-subtle">
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="planejador">A maioria dos profissionais nunca calculou. Coloque seus números abaixo e descubra quanto você ganha por hora hoje — e quanto poderia ganhar fazendo o mesmo trabalho em uma fração do tempo.</span>
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="consultor">Recorrência composta exige tempo bem investido. Coloque seus números e veja quanto cada hora sua vale hoje — e quanto poderia valer com mais fluência.</span>
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="assessor">Cliente que sai não é problema operacional — é vazamento de receita recorrente. Coloque seus números e veja quanto AUM você está perdendo por churn evitável.</span>
          <span data-profile-copy data-for="outro">A maioria dos profissionais nunca calculou. Coloque seus números abaixo e descubra quanto você ganha por hora hoje — e quanto poderia ganhar fazendo o mesmo trabalho em uma fração do tempo.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Toggle de perfil contextual — sincroniza com o da seção de Preços */}
      <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm text-subtle">
          A calculadora muda dependendo de <span class="font-semibold text-body">como você ganha dinheiro</span>. Você é…
        </p>
        <div role="radiogroup" aria-label="Perfil profissional" class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
          <button
            type="button"
            role="radio"
            aria-checked="true"
            data-profile-toggle="planejador"
            class="profile-pill rounded-full border border-border-soft bg-surface px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-subtle transition hover:border-teal/40 aria-checked:border-teal aria-checked:bg-teal-pale aria-checked:text-teal"
          >Planejador</button>
          <button
            type="button"
            role="radio"
            aria-checked="false"
            data-profile-toggle="consultor"
            class="profile-pill rounded-full border border-border-soft bg-surface px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-subtle transition hover:border-teal/40 aria-checked:border-teal aria-checked:bg-teal-pale aria-checked:text-teal"
          >Consultor</button>
          <button
            type="button"
            role="radio"
            aria-checked="false"
            data-profile-toggle="assessor"
            class="profile-pill rounded-full border border-border-soft bg-surface px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-subtle transition hover:border-teal/40 aria-checked:border-teal aria-checked:bg-teal-pale aria-checked:text-teal"
          >Assessor</button>
          <button
            type="button"
            role="radio"
            aria-checked="false"
            data-profile-toggle="outro"
            class="profile-pill rounded-full border border-border-soft bg-surface px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-subtle transition hover:border-teal/40 aria-checked:border-teal aria-checked:bg-teal-pale aria-checked:text-teal"
          >Outro</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* === CALCULADORA DE PRODUTIVIDADE: Planejador / Consultor / Outro === */}
      <div id="calc-produtividade" class="mt-12 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">

        {/* INPUTS */}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-soft bg-surface p-6 shadow-[0_12px_40px_-24px_rgba(26,26,46,0.18)]">
          <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-subtle">Seus dados</div>

          <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">Quanto você cobra por planejamento?</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <span class="text-sm text-subtle">R$</span>
                <input
                  id="calc-ticket"
                  type="text"
                  inputmode="numeric"
                  value="5.000"
                  class="ml-2 w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">Quantas horas você gasta hoje pra fazer 1 planejamento?</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-horas"
                  type="number"
                  inputmode="numeric"
                  min="1"
                  max="80"
                  step="1"
                  value="12"
                  class="w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
                <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-subtle">horas</span>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">Quantos planejamentos você entrega por mês?</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-planos"
                  type="number"
                  inputmode="numeric"
                  min="1"
                  max="100"
                  step="1"
                  value="4"
                  class="w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
                <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-subtle">/mês</span>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">Aumento de ticket esperado com material profissional</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-aumento-ticket"
                  type="range"
                  min="0"
                  max="50"
                  step="5"
                  value="20"
                  class="flex-1 accent-teal"
                />
                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 tabular-nums">
                  <span id="calc-aumento-ticket-value" class="text-base font-semibold text-dark">20</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-subtle">%</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* OUTPUTS — 4 passos paralelos à calculadora do Assessor */}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-teal/30 bg-dark p-6 text-white shadow-[0_24px_60px_-24px_rgba(13,148,136,0.4)]">
          <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-teal-light">Resultado</div>

          <div class="mt-4 space-y-5">

            {/* PASSO 1 — DOR: Tempo (HOJE vs COM AXION + DELTA) */}
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold" style="background:#FCA5A5;color:#7F1D1D">1</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider" style="color:#FCA5A5">Tempo em trabalho braçal</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pl-7">
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-3">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-soft">Hoje</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-lg font-bold tabular-nums" style="color:#FCA5A5" id="calc-out-dias-hoje">72 dias/ano</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-soft/80" id="calc-out-horas-hoje">576h/ano</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-teal/30 bg-teal/[0.08] p-3">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-teal-light">Com Karteo</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-lg font-bold tabular-nums text-teal-light" id="calc-out-dias-karteo">9 dias/ano</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-soft/80" id="calc-out-horas-karteo-tempo">72h/ano</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 pl-7 text-[12px] font-semibold text-teal-light">
                ↳ Você recupera <span id="calc-out-dias-recuperados" class="tabular-nums">63 dias úteis/ano</span> <span class="font-normal text-slate-soft" id="calc-out-semanas-recuperadas">(≈12 semanas livres)</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* PASSO 2 — STATUS: Valor da hora (HOJE vs COM AXION + MULT) */}
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-light text-[10px] font-bold text-dark">2</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-teal-light">Quanto vale sua hora</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pl-7">
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-3">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-soft">Hoje</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-lg font-bold tabular-nums text-white" id="calc-out-hora-hoje">R$ 416,67</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-soft/80">/hora</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-teal/30 bg-teal/[0.08] p-3">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-teal-light">Com Karteo</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-lg font-bold tabular-nums text-teal-light" id="calc-out-hora-karteo">R$ 3.333,33</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-soft/80">/hora</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 pl-7 text-[12px] font-semibold text-teal-light">
                ↳ Sua hora vale <span id="calc-out-mult" class="tabular-nums">8,0×</span> mais com Karteo
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* PASSO 3 — CUSTO */}
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/10 text-[10px] font-bold text-white">3</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-soft">Investimento Karteo Pro</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-1 flex items-baseline gap-2 pl-7">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold tabular-nums text-white">R$ 5.964,00</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-slate-soft">/ano · R$ 497/mês</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="h-px bg-white/15"></div>

            {/* PASSO 4 — HERÓI: Receita (HOJE vs COM AXION + DELTA) */}
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal text-[10px] font-bold text-white">4</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-teal-light">Sua receita anual</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 pl-7">
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-3">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-soft">Hoje</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-base font-bold tabular-nums text-white" id="calc-out-receita-hoje">R$ 240.000</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-teal/30 bg-teal/[0.08] p-3">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-teal-light">Com Karteo</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-base font-bold tabular-nums text-teal-light" id="calc-out-receita-potencial">R$ 288.000</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border-2 p-3" style="border-color:#16A34A;background:rgba(22,163,74,0.1)">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider" style="color:#86EFAC">Sobra no bolso</div>
                  <div class="mt-0.5 text-base font-bold tabular-nums" style="color:#86EFAC" id="calc-out-delta-receita">+ R$ 42.036</div>
                  <div class="text-[11px] text-slate-soft" id="calc-out-sobra-detalhe">já descontado Karteo</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* DIAGNÓSTICO — golpe de mestre: tempo + dinheiro juntos (já líquido) */}
            <div class="rounded-lg p-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="background:rgba(22,163,74,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(22,163,74,0.3)">
              <span class="text-teal-light font-semibold">Diagnóstico:</span>
              <span class="text-white" id="calc-out-diag"><strong>+ R$ 42.036 limpos</strong> no seu bolso (já descontado o Karteo) <em>e</em> <strong>63 dias úteis</strong> de volta no calendário. ROI <strong>7,0×</strong> só em dinheiro — o tempo é bônus.</span>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-soft">
              Premissa: 1h30 por planejamento (tempo médio real com Karteo). Aumento de ticket é hipótese controlada por você no slider — calculadora mostra teto, não garantia.
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      {/* === CALCULADORA DE CHURN: Assessor === */}
      <div id="calc-churn" class="mt-12 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">

        {/* INPUTS */}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border-soft bg-surface p-6 shadow-[0_12px_40px_-24px_rgba(26,26,46,0.18)]">
          <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-subtle">Seus dados</div>

          <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">AUM total da sua base</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <span class="text-sm text-subtle">R$</span>
                <input
                  id="calc-aum"
                  type="text"
                  inputmode="numeric"
                  placeholder="Ex.: 27.000.000"
                  class="ml-2 w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">Quantos clientes você atende?</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-clientes"
                  type="number"
                  inputmode="numeric"
                  min="1"
                  max="500"
                  step="1"
                  placeholder="Ex.: 90"
                  class="w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
                <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-subtle">clientes</span>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">Churn anual atual</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-churn-pct"
                  type="number"
                  inputmode="numeric"
                  min="1"
                  max="50"
                  step="1"
                  value="15"
                  class="w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
                <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-subtle">% /ano</span>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">ROA atual</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-roa"
                  type="number"
                  inputmode="decimal"
                  min="0.1"
                  max="5"
                  step="0.1"
                  value="1.0"
                  class="w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
                <span class="ml-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-subtle">% a.a.</span>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">% de repasse pra você</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-repasse"
                  type="number"
                  inputmode="numeric"
                  min="10"
                  max="100"
                  step="5"
                  value="50"
                  class="w-full bg-transparent text-base font-semibold text-dark tabular-nums outline-none"
                />
                <span class="ml-2 text-sm text-subtle">%</span>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="block">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-body">Redução de churn esperada com planejamento</span>
              <div class="mt-1.5 flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border-soft bg-bg-page px-4 py-2.5 focus-within:border-teal/60">
                <input
                  id="calc-reducao"
                  type="range"
                  min="10"
                  max="50"
                  step="5"
                  value="30"
                  class="flex-1 accent-teal"
                />
                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 tabular-nums">
                  <span id="calc-reducao-value" class="text-base font-semibold text-dark">30</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-subtle">%</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* OUTPUTS */}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-teal/30 bg-dark p-6 text-white shadow-[0_24px_60px_-24px_rgba(13,148,136,0.4)]">
          <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-teal-light">Resultado</div>

          {/* Estado vazio (default — antes de preencher AUM e Clientes) */}
          <div id="calc-empty-state" class="mt-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 text-center">
            <div class="text-5xl">↖️</div>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-soft">
              Preencha <span class="font-semibold text-white">AUM total</span> e <span class="font-semibold text-white">número de clientes</span> ao lado pra ver quanto o churn está custando pra você.
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Conteúdo (aparece quando há dados) */}
          <div id="calc-content" class="mt-4 space-y-5" style="display:none">

            {/* PASSO 1 — DOR */}
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold" style="background:#FCA5A5;color:#7F1D1D">1</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider" style="color:#FCA5A5">Você perde por churn hoje</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-1 flex items-baseline gap-2 pl-7">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold tabular-nums" style="color:#FCA5A5" id="calc-out-perda">R$ 0,00</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-slate-soft">/ano</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* PASSO 2 — MITIGAÇÃO */}
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-light text-[10px] font-bold text-dark">2</span>
